    {
      "id": "PopularPost353214",
      "post_content": "I do prefer a good [meltdown](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=meltdown) myself. This has the ability to continue to shut down artifacts in upcoming turns, but there's a window of time in which it can be dealt with, and in which those artifacts can be used to smack you around for a bit.  \n[Energy Flux](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Energy Flux), now there's an artifact hoser.",
      "posted_by": "Kryptnyt",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost353214\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">I do prefer a good <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"meltdown\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=meltdown\">meltdown</a> myself. This has the ability to continue to shut down artifacts in upcoming turns, but there's a window of time in which it can be dealt with, and in which those artifacts can be used to smack you around for a bit.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Energy Flux\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Energy Flux\">Energy Flux</a>, now there's an artifact hoser.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '353214'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy24840\">Kryptnyt</span>\r\n                                (12/1/2013 7:49:13 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Right